The paper discusses privacy mechanisms for event stream analysis, which involves both cryptography and database techniques. Therefore, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.DB (Databases) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of signal processing techniques, which falls under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper discusses the benefits of leveraging system theoretic techniques, which falls under cs.SI (Systems and Control).
